{"tid":610762,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Bethesda總監：別再問我上古卷軸6了 親生兒子我都不會告訴他","createTime":"2018-03-30T08:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T16:04:14.000Z","uid":66943,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0e4a05be9e5cfb7ced9d4dfd7e71c208c5644613","tid":610762,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T08:57:52.000Z","msg":"如果你在全世界最受期待的遊戲的項目組工作，當被自己的家人或者孩子反覆追問時，你會不會忍得住不劇透呢？Bethesda的總監Todd Howard就面臨著這樣嚴峻的考驗，但是對《 上古捲軸 6》這事，他守口如瓶滴水不漏。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/03/20180330_gd_340_7/gamersky_01origin_01_20183301340B7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F03%2F20180330_gd_340_7%2Fgamersky_01origin_01_20183301340B7A.jpg&h=6d3ee685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我的兒子總會問我'嗯，《上古捲軸6》甚麼時候出呀？'&rdquo;Howard在一次Blog中提到，&ldquo;然後我就會說'這個我不會說的。'他會繼續追問：'我能給你說說我對這個遊戲的想法嗎？我能去做這個遊戲嗎？拜託隨便跟我透露點吧！我不會跟任何人說的！'&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/03/20180330_gd_340_7/gamersky_02origin_03_201833013401A4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F03%2F20180330_gd_340_7%2Fgamersky_02origin_03_201833013401A4.jpg&h=33c026e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　而口密的大佬在兒子的連番追問下還是一句話：&ldquo;不管你怎麼說，我甚麼都不會說的。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　連親生仔都不說，那普通玩家想要知道《上古捲軸 6》到底有沒有在做，甚麼時候會出來，就更別提了。"},{"pid":"1eb61e162b940bfdb19865119889ad9ef81e257e","tid":610762,"uid":67346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T09:01:22.000Z","msg":"都未掠完水，咁快做為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2300033bb5e7b77e80edac8ebb04d317333baef0","tid":610762,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T09:02:09.000Z","msg":"一日mod仲有市場 一日都唔撚出繼續cap水"},{"pid":"41fc2b4289089a4a70a849870599a08a4ea704f5","tid":610762,"uid":4857,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T09:03:30.000Z","msg"